Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.47,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.57,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}C-C-Come and kick up! NOW LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.60,0:02:40.27,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}是什么悄然而至
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.88,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}传奇即将拉开序幕
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.88,0:02:45.44,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}你会喜不自胜还是鄙夷不屑？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.94,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}亦或者犹豫不决？而我心意已决  共赴这传奇
