Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.84,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}心潮澎湃  热血沸腾
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.62,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}毋庸置疑  感受波动
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.67,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}控制好敏锐的感性
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.08,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}像歌舞伎那般演绎自我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.25,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}当你深陷泥潭  是吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.93,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}何为英雄？革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.55,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}何为英雄？独领风骚
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.75,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}那是英雄！救民济世
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.70,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}你大可率性而为  逍遥自在
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.86,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}可这就是英雄的终点吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.98,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}不  艰难险阻永无止尽
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.07,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}传奇还在继续
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.24,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}坚守本心  矢志不移
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.56,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}仁义高于大义  无可辩驳
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.56,0:03:42.70,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}相信自己
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.57,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}一言九鼎  驷马难追
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.14,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}揭竿而起  掀起革命
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.76,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}挑战世界  宁死不屈
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.74,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}展翅高飞  去做那绝无仅有的异端
