Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:05.89,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}I've been walking all alone for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:12.84,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Witnessed fights and falls and never knew what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:19.88,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Searching for the answers but where am I supposed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:26.06,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}Til the age of so much I have lost.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.26,0:11:05.89,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}我踽踽独行  走过长路漫漫
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.55,0:11:12.84,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}目睹纷争与坎坷  始终难辨是非对错
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.02,0:11:19.88,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}终其一生寻找答案  却不知何去何从
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.42,0:11:26.06,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(250,250)}直至桑榆暮景  我已失去太多
